# Custom Events üì¢

Use `createEventDispatcher` to send messages up.

```javascript
import { createEventDispatcher } from 'svelte';
const dispatch = createEventDispatcher();

function sayHello() {
  dispatch('message', { text: 'Hello!' });
}
```
Listen in parent: `<Child on:message={handleMessage} />`.

# Component Example üíª

